casebody.data:
Monday, February 27, 1995

MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

94-1833. No. L-93-260. State ex rel. Babione v. Martin. Lucas County,

This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Court of Appeals for Lucas County. Upon consideration of the joint application for dismissal,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that said application be, and the same is hereby, granted.

ACCORDINGLY, IT IS FURTHER ORDERED by the court that this cause be, and hereby is, dismissed.
